snippet.textDisplay:
If you understand the true mystic meaning of Sufi Kalaam, your soul connects with the Divine Love of Allah Subhan hu Taala. In Sufi Music this Divine Love for ALLAH burst out in singers voice and it can only be happened if he or she is truly and emotionally involves in this Divine Love and fully understand the true meanings of that Kalaam. Masha Allah Atif Aslam's Sufi Music shows his maturity in his art and special interest and seriousness towards Sufi Kalaam.
ALLAH ATIF ASLAM KO IS FANN MAY KAMAAL ATA FARMAEY. AAMEEN SUMMA AAMEEN
